        <div class="section-grid" style="margin-top:1rem;">
            <div class="sub-card">
                <div class="sub-title"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Overview</div>
                <p style="font-size:.78rem;color:#334155;margin:0;">
                    The final step in the commission pipeline. Calls the stored procedure
                    <code>lcs_incentive.ProcessFinalCommission</code> on the MIS server,
                    which pushes finalized commission data to the MIS/salary incentive ledger.
                    On success, inserts a lock record in <code>is_final_commission_process</code>
                    to prevent re-processing. If MIS source tables have no data (0 rows returned),
                    the step is marked <strong>NoData</strong> — not an error, fully re-runnable.
                </p>
                <div style="margin-top:.65rem; display:flex; gap:.4rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
                    <span class="tag tag-blue">Stored Procedure Call</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-red">Month Lock</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-orange">MIS Integration</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-purple">NoData Safe</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-card">
                <div class="sub-title"><i class="fas fa-server"></i> Server &amp; Connections</div>
                <div class="server-box main">
